comment: Why can't we scan paper coupons to the app? Has a Print View but you can't print coupons. Huh? Filters don't work. Even with the Clicklist stuff unchecked in filters it still shows up in the coupon list. Now we have to wade through all the coupons that are ONLY for Clicklist. (Only 8 people on the planet are interested in clicklist so why do we have all those coupons interspersed with regular coupons?). A complete waste of time.

author: Kelly Elizabeth
comment: This is the most tedious way to put together a list of items for purchase.  It would take less time to just go to the store and wander the aisles. But there's so many items you miss when looking only at sale items.
